(na makikita mo lang sa salamin)

00:09:19.940 --> 00:09:21.160
(at hindi man lang mahawakan?)

00:09:21.230 --> 00:09:23.100
(Bakit sila nakatambak dito
tulad ng karaniwang mga gulay?)

00:09:23.420 --> 00:09:24.990
(At pinapayagan akong hawakan sila nang malaya?)

00:09:25.420 --> 00:09:26.260
